or we could do:
```scala
val semanticDBDoc = semanticdbs.textDocument(source).documentIncludingStale
if(semanticDBDoc.isEmpty){
  warnings.noSemanticdb(source)
} else {
  val occurrence = for { ...} yield occ
  occurrence match {
    case None =>
      // ignore
    case Some(occ) =>
      (...)
  }
}
```
